                        <h4>PTZ Control: Kommandos</h4>

                        <p>IN-3005, IN-3010, IN-3011</p>

                        <div class="code shadow">
                        <code><pre>
                        &lt;Makes&gt;
                            &lt;Make Name="INSTAR" Model="IN-301x" &#47;&gt;
                        &lt;&#47;Makes&gt;
                        &lt;CommandURL&gt;&#47;decoder_control.cgi&lt;&#47;CommandURL&gt;
                        &lt;Commands&gt;
                           &lt;Center&gt;command=25&lt;&#47;Center&gt;
                           &lt;Left&gt;command=4&lt;&#47;Left&gt;
